          exact Or.inr ⟨y, rfl⟩

        -- Case x = eLao

    intro a b h

          rw [add_comm]

          <;> aesop

          simp_all [add_comm, add_assoc, add_left_comm, apd_zero, addsNucA, MΘNae.rec]
          <;> aesop
        contradiction
